### Coffee — Dapr Workflow demo
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client and JetBrains HTTP Client.
### Run `make dev` first; the HTTP server listens on :8000 (Tilt port-forward).

@host = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Brew a cup
# @name brew
POST {{host}}/v1/coffee
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "beans": "arabica",
  "size":  "large"
}

### 2. Peek at the running workflow (uses the id from request #1)
GET {{host}}/v1/coffee/{{brew.response.body.instanceId}}

### 3. Peek by id (paste manually if needed)
@instance_id = paste-id-here
GET {{host}}/v1/coffee/{{instance_id}}
